A '''reversed repulsorfield''', also known as a '''man trap''',<ref name="SAV">[[Scum and Villainy (sourcebook)|''Scum and Villainy'']]</ref> was a restraining device that utilized multiple [[gravfield generator]]s to create an immobilizing [[Gravity/Legends|gravity]] field that easily prevented victims from moving yet without harming them.<ref name="EGWT">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref>

